// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0334 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c6cc22e3-897b-54e9-bf19-64e08fbd4712

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
